<HEAD>SOCIETY of CINCINNATI.</HEAD>
<P>VOTED, that Maj. SEYMOUR, and Mr. BEERS, be, and they are hereby appointed a Committee to wait on Mr. WATERMAN, and re|turn him the Thanks of this Society for his ORATION delivered before them this Day, and to request a Co|py of the same for publication, at the Expence of said Society.</P>
